Step 1: Create Spring Boot Project in Eclipse
1. Open Eclipse
2. Go to File → New → Spring Starter Project
3. Enter the following:
Name: SBHW
Type: Maven
Group: SBHWGr
Artifact: SBHW
Description: SB HW
Package: SBHWGr.SBHW
Packaging: Jar
Java Version: 17 or higher
Dependencies: Select only ✅ Spring Web
4. Click Finish
Eclipse will create and build the project.





